title: Fort McHenry National Monument and Historic Shrine: Places To Go
body: Explore This Park    Plan Your Visit     Places To Go             Places To Go       The Visitor Center includes an orientation film, exhibits, gift shop and restrooms. The Museums include the fort, barracks and related structures. The barracks contain several exhibits: The Enlistmen's Quarters; an Electronic Map; uniform and weapons displays; videos; Junior Officers' Quarters; powder magazine; Commanding Officer's Quarters; and the 1814 Guard House.
